{
  "stem": "12053.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She has got very definite memories of those days when our home was disbanded, you know, when all the things were sort of more or less given away instead of sold.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents moved into the Jewish hospital for safety.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did the laundry then because of their profession.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took over the laundry because the staff had to leave in the Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they was sort of as safe as can be for three-- for two or three years, till 1942.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister had to go and live with a, a half Jewish couple.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she went to see my parents after school in the, in the Jewish hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she has different recollections, again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because things were much tougher for her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they reopened the school in a small way, classrooms to teach the children again afterwards.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, for me, there was no more schooling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In fact, my schooling really finished when I-- finished when I was 14.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because that was the time when they finished the [NON-ENGLISH] and we weren't allowed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then there was something called [NON-ENGLISH] that was twice a week, for a few hours twice a week.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was a general thing for all German children, Jewish or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And for that, we had two classes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was Jewish again in Jewish classrooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was the schooling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Apart from that, I helped my parents in the business from the age of 14 until I left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went from Munich through Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we picked up more children on the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all went via [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the last stop into Holland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody who went by train went via Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was a fantastic feeling, that we left Germany behind you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You breathed free.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
